OL,3,CMPs to consider reduced drink-drive
OL,4,Climit and tests for drivers over 70
OL,6,FThe drink-drive limit may be reduced
OL,7,Fand drivers over the age of 70 could
OL,8,Fface mandatory tests as part of an
OL,9,Foverhaul of road safety laws.
OL,11,FMinisters are set to consider whether
OL,12,Fcompulsory eye tests should be
OL,13,Fintroduced every three years for
OL,14,Fdrivers over the age of 70 with people
OL,15,Fto be banned from driving if they
OL,16,Ffail, according to a report in The
OL,17,FTimes.
OL,19,FThe UK is one of only three European
OL,20,Fcountries to rely on self-reporting of
OL,21,Feyesight problems that affect driving.
