OL,6,FUnder the reported plans being
OL,7,Fconsidered by Transport Secretary
OL,8,FHeidi Alexander, the drink-drive limit
OL,9,Fin England and Wales will also be
OL,10,Freduced to come into line with
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,FThe drink-drive blood alcohol limit is
OL,14,Fcurrently 0.05 per cent in Scotland,
OL,15,Fcompared to 0.08 per cent in England
OL,16,Fand Wales.
OL,18,FMinisters will also consider tougher
OL,19,Fpenalties for uninsured drivers and
OL,20,Fpeople failing to wear a seatbelt.
