OL,6,FThe proposal, which is due to be
OL,7,Fpublished and consulted on in Autumn,
OL,8,Fis also expected to allow police to
OL,9,Fprosecute for drug-driving based on
OL,10,Froadside saliva tests rather than
OL,11,Fblood tests.
OL,13,FAA president Edmund King said it was
OL,14,F"much overdue".
OL,16,F"We believe these new measures will
OL,17,Fnot only modernise our approach to
OL,18,Fsaving lives but also provide renewed
OL,19,Fmomentum in making our roads safer for
OL,20,Feveryone," he said.
