OL,6,FHe added while vision checks for older
OL,7,Fdrivers could "make a real
OL,8,Fdifference", failing to introduce
OL,9,Frestrictions on newly-licenced drivers
OL,10,Ftransporting young people was "a major
OL,11,Foversight".
OL,13,FIAM RoadSmart director of policy and
OL,14,Fstandards Nicholas Lyes also welcomed
OL,15,Fan update to the road safety strategy
OL,16,Fbut said more resources were needed.
