OL,6,F"While many drivers over the age of 70
OL,7,Fare safe and competent, health issues
OL,8,Fand confidence can have an impact on
OL,9,Fdriving abilities, so it is sensible
OL,10,Fto review whether changes need to be
OL,11,Fmade," he said.
OL,13,F"We would also support reducing the
OL,14,Fdrink-drive limit in England and Wales
OL,15,Falongside measures to target drug-
OL,16,Fdriving, however these would require
OL,17,Fsignificantly more backing for roads
OL,18,Fpolicing teams to effectively enforce
OL,19,Fnew laws."
